<i>adverb</i>: 꾹꾹 [꾹꾹], 꾹 [꾹], 꼭꼭 [꼭꼭], 꼭 [꼭] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>꾹꾹 [꾹꾹]</dt><br>
<dd>1. firmly; hard</dd><br>
<dd>잇따라 또는 매우 힘을 주어 누르거나 조이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of pressing down, gripping, or tightening very strongly or repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. patiently; stoically</dd><br>
<dd>잇따라 또는 몹시 힘을 들여 참거나 견디는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of enduring or bearing very painfully or repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dd>3. completely</dd><br>
<dd>아주 단단히 숨거나 어떤 곳에 들어가서 나오지 않는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of hiding or not entirely coming out of a place.</dd><br>
<dt>꾹 [꾹]</dt><br>
<dd>1. firmly; hard</dd><br>
<dd>매우 힘주어 세게 누르거나 잡거나 조이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of pressing down, gripping, or tightening very strongly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. patiently; stoically</dd><br>
<dd>매우 애써서 힘들게 참거나 견디는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of enduring or bearing very painfully.</dd><br>
<dd>3. completely</dd><br>
<dd>조금도 보이지 않게 숨거나 한 곳에서 나오지 않는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of hiding or not coming out of a place so as not to be seen.</dd><br>
<dt>꼭꼭 [꼭꼭]</dt><br>
<dd>1. firmly; tightly</dd><br>
<dd>잇따라 힘주어 세게 누르거나 잡는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of pressing repeatedly or holding strongly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. patiently; stoically</dd><br>
<dd>잇따라 힘들여 참거나 견디는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of painfully enduring or bearing one after another.</dd><br>
<dd>3. completely</dd><br>
<dd>잇따라 보이지 않게 숨거나 한 곳에서 나오지 않는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of repeatedly hiding or not coming out of a place so as not to be seen.</dd><br>
<dt>꼭 [꼭]</dt><br>
<dd>1. firmly; tightly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것을 빈틈이 없이 힘주어 세게 누르거나 잡는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of pressing or holding something strongly and fast.</dd><br>
<dd>2. patiently; stoically</dd><br>
<dd>애써서 힘들여 참거나 견디는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of enduring or bearing something in spite of pain.</dd><br>
<dd>3. completely</dd><br>
<dd>보이지 않게 숨거나 한 곳에서 나오지 않는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of hiding or not coming out of a place so as not to be seen.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>